"It's https://github.com/scikit-hep/boost-histogram/issues/423 - while Hist does have intimate knowledge of boost-histogram types, and as such could add custom handling for each type, it would be better to build on the boost-histogram Protocol that Uproot, histoprint, mplhep, and Physt need as well.\n\nThanks @henryiii. cc @andrzejnovak as I see that https://github.com/scikit-hep/boost-histogram/issues/423 is relevant to him as well.\n\nAny workaround for now? \n\nThis has been solved with the PlottableHistogram Protocol, coming in the next release of boost-histogram and Hist 2.1. Hoping for right before the holidays."